  <brief_title>Health Related QOL, Depression and Lifestyle Changes in Insulin Resistant Adolescents</brief_title>
  <official_title>Health-Related Quality of Life, Depression and the Impact on Successful Incorporation of Lifestyle Changes in Insulin Resistant Adolescents as Evidenced by Changes in BMI, Waist Circumference and Metabolic Parameters</official_title>
